      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/2426814e-b40c-11e2-b8f6-52540035b04c).  Ran 3 tests.  1 tests failed: racer.",
