      },
      "date": "2013-05-03 18:15:19.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThe 30-minute racer test didn't pass, but I didn't fully expect that to happen.  The main effort was to verify that this patch didn't break anything in racer, and possibly hit the LASSERT() in question by luck.\n\nI think the patch is OK for landing, and hopefully the next time this LASSERTF() is hit we'll get a bit more information and useful debug logs.",
